255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 库目录：/usr/local/lib/python3.3</p><p><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>Windows下</strong></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">一、下载</span></strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 文件名：python-3.3.2.amd64.msi</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 下载地址：<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.python.org/download/releases/3.3.2/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 153); text-decoration: none;\">http://www.python.org/download/releases/3.3.2/</a></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">二、安装</span>